
                     B u n d l e - O p e n I L S
                   -----------------------------


The Bundle::OpenILS collection is a set of Perl modules bundled to
ease installation overhead for Open-ILS (http://open-ils.org),
an open-source integrated library system developed by Georgia
Library Pines (http://pines.lib.ga.us/)

PREREQUISITES

Not a complete list yet.

  Yaz toolkit
  Apache2
  mod_perl2
  PostgreSQL

INSTALLATION

Near as I can tell, the only way to install a bundle is from CPAN
like this:

perl -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::OpenILS'

DOCUMENTATION

See documentation for individual modules included.

SUPPORT

Coming in next version :-)

